s":"bowl, thermal serving bowl or other large bowl","hintsAndTricks":["This recipe is very popular in Molise and Abruzzo.","Please refer to <i>The Basic Cookbook<\/i> for the Vegetable stock paste recipe.","Pasta that is cooked al dente is tender but still firm to the bite."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","35m","6 portions"]}